All Implemented Interfaces:
edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.DirectedGraph<Vertex,java.lang.Integer>, edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.Graph<Vertex,java.lang.Integer>, edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.Hypergraph<Vertex,java.lang.Integer>, java.io.Serializable
public class DirectedCorpusGraph
extends edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.AbstractTypedGraph<Vertex,java.lang.Integer>
implements edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.DirectedGraph<Vertex,java.lang.Integer>

Implementacia directed grafu urcena pre corpus, velmy velky graf. Tento graf vyuziva rozne predpoklady, ak nebudu splnena moze to viest k nespravnemu spravaniu. Predpoklady vyuziva k rychlejsiemu spracovaniu.

Author:
Lukas Sekerak
